---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import business from "../assets/business.jpg";
---

<div class="flex flex-col items-center w-full border md:my-10">
  <div class="max-w-lg px-2">
    <h2
      class="scroll-mt-10 md:py-6 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight first:mt-0 capitalize mb-2"
    >
      Freedom Fiberglass Pools
    </h2>
    <p class="my-4 text-gray-600">
      We have made over 70,000 pools TODO and are proud to have an innovative
      range of designs, colors and surface finishes. You can choose from 30 pool
      models from small to large, in 10 stunning pool colors and all with
      superior ColorGuard surface protection. We have been leading the industry
      in product development and technology to ensure every Aqua Technics
      fiberglass pool is built stronger to last longer. release models. TODO
    </p>
    <div>
      <Image
        class="object-contain w-full h-full"
        src={business}
        alt="picture of our company"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-2 justify-evenly w-full my-4">
      <a
        href="/range"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-3 mb-2 text-xl text-white bg-sky-950 rounded-md hover:bg-sky-800 sm:w-auto sm:mb-0"
      >
        Pools
      </a>
      <a
        href="/colors"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-3 mb-2 text-xl text-white bg-sky-950 rounded-md hover:bg-sky-800 sm:w-auto sm:mb-0"
      >
        Colors
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
